  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">A Recipe for Reducing Ivory Consumption in China</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project will build on the foundation of previous demand reduction campaigns, aiming to activate the public to engage in anti-ivory campaigns themselves. This will include: harnessing the power of social media, building on a pilot (&quot;voices of China&quot;); working with corporate leaders; research work to further explain the rationale for restricting the legal market for ivory and promoting this work to Chinese officials and the Chinese public.</narrative>
  </description>
